window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>One man's pursuit of the truth turns his world upside down in this international best-selling thriller.</b></p> <p>Martin Briar drags himself through life, having lost the will to live since the disappearance of his 12-year-old daughter two decades ago.</p> <p>With depression again rearing its ugly head, he meets a peculiar antique dealer who offers him the chance to find out what happened to his only child. Martin wants nothing more than to answer the questions that have haunted his every waking moment all these years.</p> <p>This once in a lifetime opportunity proves irresistible, but is Martin prepared for the answer - and the cost - of discovering the truth?</p> <p><i>Wealth of Time</i> is the international best-selling first novel in the Wealth of Time Series. If you enjoy fast-paced thrillers, twists and turns, and a cunning villain, then youâ€™ll love this high-octane series from Andre Gonzalez!</p> <p>Buy <i>Wealth of Time</i> today to join an ordinary man in his quest for the truth!</p>"; 
